&quot;. O t r o m a t e r i a l i d e n t i f i c a d o c o m o 
<taxonomicName authorityName="PEREZ" authorityYear="1897" box="[739,915,709,730]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Lithurgus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="113" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sublaevis">
<emphasis box="[739,915,709,730]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">Lithurgus sublaevis</emphasis>
